{"id":483677,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/No_Pads%2C_No_Helmets...Just_Balls","text":"\"No Pads, No Helmets...Just Balls\" is the first studio album by Canadian pop punk band, Simple Plan. \"No Pads, No Helmets...Just Balls\" was released on March 19, 2002 through both Atlantic and Lava.\nThe album debuted at #35 on the \"Billboard\" 200 and at #8 on the Canadian Albums Chart. The album was certified 2\u00D7 Platinum by the RIAA.\nThe album featured the singles \"I'm Just a Kid\", \"I'd Do Anything\", \"Addicted\", and \"Perfect\".","categories":[],"infobox_types":["Album"],"annotations":[{"uri":"Studio_album","surface_form":"studio album","offset":48},{"uri":"Pop_punk","surface_form":"pop punk","offset":73},{"uri":"Simple_Plan","surface_form":"Simple Plan","offset":88},{"uri":"Atlantic_Records","surface_form":"Atlantic","offset":180},{"uri":"Lava_Records","surface_form":"Lava","offset":193},{"uri":"Billboard_200","surface_form":"\"Billboard\" 200","offset":231},{"uri":"Canadian_Albums_Chart","surface_form":"Canadian Albums Chart","offset":264},{"uri":"RIAA_certification","surface_form":"Platinum","offset":314},{"uri":"Recording_Industry_Association_of_America","surface_form":"RIAA","offset":330},{"uri":"I%27m_Just_a_Kid","surface_form":"I'm Just a Kid","offset":368},{"uri":"I%27d_Do_Anything_(Simple_Plan_song)","surface_form":"I'd Do Anything","offset":386},{"uri":"Addicted_(Simple_Plan_song)","surface_form":"Addicted","offset":405},{"uri":"Perfect_(Simple_Plan_song)","surface_form":"Perfect","offset":421}]}